title: shake and vibration from the speaker on pixel 4a?
content:
I have exchanged 2 pixel 4a devices. 
I have been experiencing the strange shake and vibration from the speaker sounds on TWO BRAND NEW pixel 4a DEVICES.

I have been buying way too many google phones in the last 10 years. This is the most strangest problem in a NEW google device. 

AND YES, I HAVE TRIED ALL TROUBLESHOOTING STEPS OF RESETTING, SAFE MODES, AND ALL THE REST. THE PROBLEM IS PERSISTENT ON BOTH NEW DEVICES
